ride.path

Class FastestPathComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • ride.path.StationComparator
      • ride.path.FastestPathComparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator<Station>

    public class FastestPathComparator
extends StationComparator
    This class is used to compare stations according to the time spent to go from start to the Station by foot and from the Station to returnPoint by bicycle. It is used to find the best station to start a ride.
    Author:
    Pietro Dellino
    See Also:
    StationComparator, PathStrategy, FastestPathStrategy
